## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of recent data and the potential bias in opinion pieces. The complexity of political division means that not all factors can be comprehensively covered in a single report. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may introduce interpretation biases. Further research could benefit from primary data collection and analysis to provide a more nuanced understanding of the issue.